  <title>
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">CLIMANDES &#x2013; Servicios Clim&#xE1;ticos con &#xC9;nfasis en los Andes en Apoyo a las Decisiones</narrative>
  </title>
  <description type="1">
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">An indispensable cornerstone for achieving effective adaptation and reducing the impacts of climate variability is the availability of efficient and reliable climate services. On the basis of the achievements to date, the second phase of CLIMANDES will continue contributing to the development of the Global Framework for Climate Services (GFCS) in the Andean region. Improved climate services will support climate-smart decisions in the key economic agricultural sector, from which the poorest segments of the population and societies at large will be able to benefit.</narrative>
  </description>
